# Inference Rules
# TypeDB inference rules for governance automation
# Part of: EPIC-DR-012 Schema Modularization
# Created: 2026-01-17
# Updated: 2026-01-17 - Disabled for TypeDB 3.x migration (rules → functions)
#
# NOTE: TypeDB 3.x replaces "rule ... when ... then ..." with functions.
# These rules are disabled until they can be migrated to 3.x function syntax.
# See: https://typedb.com/docs/typeql/functions
# GAP-TYPEDB-INFERENCE-001: Migrate inference rules to TypeDB 3.x functions

# No define block - all rules are disabled for 3.x migration

